The Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer course at 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week program that prepares students for a career in data science. With no previous knowledge required, students will learn Python, SQL, and other tools to become professional data analysts. They will explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees and work with supervised and unsupervised learning models. The course also focuses on developing AI projects from development to deployment and maintenance. Classes are held three times a week with a maximum class size of 12 students. The course offers certificates recognized by multiple organizations. No previous experience is needed, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. Stop.